OL,3,CChannel Islands' night-time economy
OL,4,Cstruggling in cost of living crisis
OL,6,FA Guernsey bar manager says the cost
OL,7,Fof living crisis is proving
OL,8,Fdetrimental to the Channel Islands'
OL,9,Fnight-time economy.
OL,11,FJake McCombe, manager of JB Parker's
OL,12,FBar and Wine Cellar in St Peter Port,
OL,13,Fsays the number of people going for a
OL,14,Fnight out on the town has decreased
OL,15,Fmarkedly since the Covid pandemic.
OL,17,FMr McCombe told ITV News: "Hospitality
OL,18,Fhas definitely changed, especially in
OL,19,FGuernsey post-Covid, and with the cost
OL,20,Fof living crisis our costs go up all
OL,21,Fthe time.
