OL,3,CChannel Islands' night-time economy
OL,4,Cstruggling in cost of living crisis
OL,6,F"You can notice on the weekend there
OL,7,Fis much less footfall in town.
OL,8,FUsually, you would see streams and
OL,9,Fstreams of people but sometimes it
OL,10,Fcould be an empty street or it could
OL,11,Fbe a Thursday and packed. It's
OL,12,Fcompletely unpredictable.
OL,14,F"You can see people are much more
OL,15,Fcareful about what they spend and when
OL,16,Fthey spend it."
OL,18,FHe added: "I'm very good friends with
OL,19,Fthe managers or owners of most of the
OL,20,Flocal restaurants and bars and they
OL,21,Ffeel the same pinch.
