OL,3,CChannel Islands' night-time economy
OL,4,Cstruggling in cost of living crisis
OL,6,FMr McCombe also says that the cost of
OL,7,Falcohol has gone up significantly,
OL,8,Fcausing many to think twice about
OL,9,Fgoing out.
OL,11,FThis is not the first time the cost of
OL,12,Fliving crisis has hit the night-time
OL,13,Feconomy in the Channel Islands.
OL,15,FIn November 2023, Guernsey saw taxi
OL,16,Ffares rise by 7.67% due to the high
OL,17,Frate of inflation. In real terms, it
OL,18,Fmeans a ride now costs an extra 30p
OL,19,Fper mile for passengers.
