OL,4,Cstruggling in cost of living crisis
OL,6,FJersey also saw its taxi prices rise
OL,7,Fby roughly 12% in July 2023.
OL,9,FRojo, a popular nightclub in St
OL,10,FHelier, will close after a 12-hour
OL,11,Ffarewell party on Saturday 27 July
OL,12,Fafter being in business for almost 20
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FThe club's owners say going out for a
OL,16,Fdrink is now unaffordable for many.
